00:06:40.100 --> 00:06:40.610
No.

00:06:41.140 --> 00:06:41.980
Porque tengo una cita con Danica

00:06:41.980 --> 00:06:43.040
para jugar al Go.

00:06:43.220 --> 00:06:44.000
Últimamente

00:06:44.000 --> 00:06:45.400
