00:07:17.860 --> 00:07:19.160
De todos modos, nuestra empresa...

00:07:21.060 --> 00:07:21.930
Disculpa.

00:07:25.860 --> 00:07:26.480
Diga, Director Shen.

00:07:27.460 --> 00:07:28.000
Qin Xiang,

00:07:28.260 --> 00:07:29.100
